# 1Password Secret References
# ==========================
# Format: ENV_VAR="op://vault/item/field"
# Note: Quotes required for vault/item names with spaces
#
# Example: GITHUB_TOKEN="op://Claude Code Tools/GitHub Token/token"
#
# Usage:
#   1. Add your secret mappings below
#   2. Tools using run-with-secrets will inject these as env vars
#   3. User approves each access via Touch ID / YubiKey
#
# Setup:
#   1. Create vault "Claude Code Tools" in 1Password
#   2. Add items to the vault
#   3. Map them here using op:// references

# Example mappings (uncomment and customize):
# GITHUB_TOKEN="op://Claude Code Tools/GitHub Token/token"
# LINEAR_API_KEY="op://Claude Code Tools/Linear/api_key"
# DATABASE_URL="op://Claude Code Tools/Database/connection_string"
# AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID="op://Claude Code Tools/AWS/access_key"
# AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY="op://Claude Code Tools/AWS/secret_key"
